{
  "stem": "11552.4",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I was still not sure what was happening, so my mother and I decided that I would go in first to Buczacz and find out if things were OK.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then she will come.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went in and I met my friend Slavka, and she brought me to her home.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was going to sleep with her in her bedroom, but I couldn't sleep on a bed-- wasn't used to sleeping on a bed anymore.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I turned and tossed, and turned and tossed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened is, I went to beg for food, and the people told me that the Russians are here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, I didn't know it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I went to look on the street, and on the road, and there they were, traveling.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Russians were traveling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What did I-- I-- I-- I can tell you, I was very happy, but remember, there was something very important about us-- that was not a rejoicing, time of rejoicing.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was a time of facing the truth, because when we were trying to survive, when we're fighting to survive, we were aware of what happened, but we didn't let it into our-- our minds to extent where it will drive us crazy.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But when the liberation came and we were finally free, the tragedy hit us with full power.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, I was 13, not even 14 years old when I was liberated, because my birthday was in May, and that was March",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
